{"type": "article", "id": 5819, "title": "灯塔灯具系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-03T07:36:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234016Wi6pSn85sXJkRT9z.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在今年的巴黎国际家居装饰博览会上，英国设计师 Benjamin Hubert 带来了推出了一系列名为灯塔的灯具，考虑的最核心的问题即是如何将传统玻璃制作流程运用到灯具的设计中去。整个灯塔系列都是由两个简单优雅的吹制玻璃组成，不过外部却形态不一。手工吹制的玻璃表面用磨床进行切割，并加以磨砂喷面，以更好的捕捉聚散效果，灯光通过内部组件进行投射，反映到外部表面上，每一种都创造了不同类型的灯光和阴影。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340140f29JptHOIlrwyzu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340142FdoKZNpPDcb175C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234014ta2FQudSOw5mgRJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.090625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234015u0aw23GhoOWeNlKX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340152IOzXuQhVULCgnmk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234016gyGISp0JPr14t7DH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}